title: 1974 Cupa României Final
text: The 1974 Cupa României Final was the 36th final of <a href="Romania">Romania</a>'s most prestigious <a href="Association%20football">football</a> cup competition. It was disputed between <a href="CSM%20Jiul%20Petro%C8%99ani">Jiul Petroşani</a> and <a href="FC%20Politehnica%20Timi%C8%99oara">Politehnica Timișoara</a>, and was won by <a href="CSM%20Jiul%20Petro%C8%99ani">Jiul Petroşani</a> after a game with 6 goals. It was the first cup for <a href="CSM%20Jiul%20Petro%C8%99ani">Jiul Petroşani</a>.
